    50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
}
```

## Print Mode Badge Expansion

In print, badges show their names inline:
```css
@media print {
    .tool-badge {
        width: auto;
        height: auto;
        padding: 2px 8px;
        background: white;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        font-size: 0.65rem;
    }

    .tool-badge-icon {
        display: none; /* Hide icon in print */
    }

    .tool-badge::after {
        content: attr(data-tool-name);
    }

    .tool-badge.tool-success::before {
        content: '✓ ';
        color: green;
    }

    .tool-badge.tool-error::before {
        content: '✗ ';
        color: red;
    }
}
```

## Overflow Badge Expanded State

When user clicks "+X more", show all badges:
```css
.message-header-right.expanded {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    max-height: none;
}

.message-header-right.expanded .tool-badge {
    display: inline-flex; /* Show hidden badges */
}

.message-header-right:not(.expanded) .tool-badge:nth-child(n+7) {
    display: none; /* Hide after 6th badge */
}

.tool-overflow {
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
}

.message-header-right.expanded .tool-overflow {
    order: 999; /* Move to end */
}
```

## Popover Syntax Highlighting

Tool input/output often contains JSON or code:
```css
.tool-popover-content code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    background: oklch(0.1 0.015 260);
    padding: 2px 4px;
    border-radius: 2px;
}

.tool-popover-content pre {
    margin: 0;
    padding: var(--space-2);
    background: oklch(0.1 0.015 260);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    overflow-x: auto;
    max-height: 200px;
}

.tool-popover-content .json-key { color: var(--primary); }
.tool-popover-content .json-string { color: var(--green); }
.tool-popover-content .json-number { color: var(--amber); }
```

